 {"id":"bd-3m5","title":"Robot output unit tests + e2e validation scripts","description":"WHAT: Comprehensive test coverage for all robot output changes in this epic. THREE layers: (1) Unit tests for each new field/struct — verify serialization shape, field presence, correct types, default values. (2) Conformance tests comparing Rust JSON output against Go reference fixtures for every robot mode (--robot-triage, --robot-plan, --robot-insights, --robot-next, --robot-priority). (3) E2e bash script (scripts/test_robot_output_parity.sh) that runs both bv and bvr against a shared test fixture, diffs the JSON schemas field-by-field, and logs discrepancies with context. LOGGING: Each test should print what it's checking, expected vs actual, and on failure dump the full JSON for debugging. E2e script should use set -euo pipefail, trap for cleanup, and produce a summary report at the end. ACCEPTANCE: All robot outputs have matching JSON schemas. Zero field-name or type mismatches. E2e script passes with exit 0. Conformance fixtures updated. PARENT: bd-1ru","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:25:36.467310033Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-08T00:28:11.780541973Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3m5","depends_on_id":"bd-1ru.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:11.094387354Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3m5","depends_on_id":"bd-1ru.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:11.635123738Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3m5","depends_on_id":"bd-1ru.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:11.951541878Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3m5","depends_on_id":"bd-1ru.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:12.461815380Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3m5","depends_on_id":"bd-1ru